visual_elements.description: Plan view diagram of a carport parking space showing a top-down view of a car parked between two corner columns. Dimensions indicate a minimum 20 feet open space lengthwise and an open width dimension. The driveway/parking surface is labeled adjacent to the parking space.

Left side elevation view of a covered parking space showing a car under a roof supported by two corner columns. The bottom roof system is labeled with a minimum clearance of 7 feet open height and a minimum 20 feet open width.
visual_elements.location: top right side of the page

visual_elements.description: Front elevation view of a covered parking space showing a car under a sloped roof supported by two corner columns. The bottom roof system is labeled with a minimum clearance of 7 feet open height and a minimum 10 feet open width.
visual_elements.location: bottom right side of the page
